            <h2 class="mt-4 text-display font-bold text-white">When Hookdeck Isn't Enough</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-body-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Hookdeck does one thing well: receiving and routing webhooks. But there are clear cases where it falls short.
            </p>
